description:
&lt;p&gt;The Improvement Directorate’s purpose is to embed an improvement approach and culture across the NHS in England which enables and empowers staff, organisations and systems to support services to become better and safer for patients.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The PA to Directors role is a key part of the Corporate Office and is responsible for the provision of efficient and effective administrative support to the Director(s). This post holder will need to provide managerial and administrative support to the Director of products and services and the Director of engagement and implementation team.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Shortlisting will be completed within one week of the advert closing, with interviews taking place during the following fortnight (ie within 3 weeks of the advert close date).&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Please note that the reason for the fixed term of this contract is to cover maternity leave.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;NameDebbie BarnhurstJob titleSenior Business ManagerEmail addressdeborah.barnhurst@nhs.netAdditional contact information&lt;/p&gt;
